 A = \begin{bmatrix}1 & 1 \\ -1 & 1\end{bmatrix}, \quad \tilde{A} = \begin{bmatrix}1 & 1 \\ 0 & 1\end{bmatrix}, 
 \|A\|_2 = \sqrt{2}\approx 1.4142, \qquad  \|\tilde{A}\|_2 = \sqrt{\frac{\sqrt{5}+3}{2}}\approx 1.6180. 
\|\tilde{A}\|_F < \|A\|_F
\|\tilde{A}\|_{\star} \leq \|A\|_{\star}
\star = 1,\infty
